ESRI_ItemInformation.name: USA Major Cities
ESRI_ItemInformation.snippet: This group layer presents the locations of cities within the United States with populations of approximately 10,000 or greater, all state capitals, and the national capital.
ESRI_ItemInformation.description: This group layer presents the locations of cities within United States with populations of 10,000 or greater (based on Census 2010 figures), all state capitals, and the national capital. Its layers symbolize the cities by population class (based on 2014 population) using manual classification method.
ESRI_ItemInformation.summary: This group layer presents the locations of cities within the United States with populations of approximately 10,000 or greater, all state capitals, and the national capital.
